        <p>High-quality genomes from the IMG/VR v3 database for which a host prediction was obtained with iPHoP (score ≥90) were binned based on the average amino acid identity (AAI) to the closest reference in NCBI RefSeq Virus r203 (x-axis). Predictions entirely based on host-based tools are indicated as “Host only,” predictions exclusively based on RaFAH are indicated as “Phage only,” and predictions where both types of tools were consistent and with iPHoP score ≥90 are listed as “Both.” Source data are available in <xref rid="pbio.3002083.s021" ref-type="supplementary-material">S1 Data</xref> (Source data 4).</p>
